import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import {Container, Form, Card, Row, Button, Image, Col} from 'react-bootstrap';
const ExploreSearchComponent = () => {
  render(
    <Card style={{width: '90%', margin: 20}}>
      <Card.Header as="h5">EXPLORE CANADA</Card.Header>
      <Form
        inline
        style={{
          paddingLeft: 20,
          paddingRight: 20,
          paddingTop: 10,
          paddingBottom: 10,
        }}
      >
        <Form.Row style={{width: '100%'}}>
          <Col lg={4}>
            <Form.Control
              type="text"
              placeholder="SEARCH BY CITY NAME"
              style={{width: '100%', marginTop: 10}}
            />
          </Col>
          <Col lg={6} style={{}}>
            <Form.Row
              controlId="formfGroupCheckIn"
              style={{
                width: '100%',
                marginTop: 10,
              }}
            >
              <Form.Label
                style={{fontSize: 14, fontWeight: 'bold', width: '20%'}}
              >
                Check In
              </Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                type="date"
                placeholder="Start Date"
                style={{width: '30%'}}
              />
              <Form.Label
                style={{fontSize: 14, fontWeight: 'bold', width: '20%'}}
              >
                Check Out
              </Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                type="date"
                placeholder="End Date"
                style={{width: '30%'}}
              />
            </Form.Row>
          </Col>

          <Col lg={2}>
            <Button style={{width: '100%', height: 38, marginTop: 10}}>
              Search
            </Button>
          </Col>
        </Form.Row>
      </Form>
    </Card>
  );
};

export default ExploreSearchComponent;
